    "However, despite the remarkable results, the identified gestures are rather simple and discretized, rendering the control less natural whilst requiring high power consumption 39.",
    "Improvements can be achieved by increasing the invasiveness of the approach, depending on the specific type of amputation.",
    "For high-level amputations, Targeted Muscle Reinnervation (TMR) 156, 157 can provide a suitable surgical technique to enable prosthesis control using EMG signals.",
